      <title>A message from @eobofficial: I have a new solo album coming out on 22nd May. It ...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DV_IY5zjAf7/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/652765451_886044817770760_5171870049393475269_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NDgzNjcwMTc2MDA2MzQ4Mw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=PUTwYjecXlsQ7kNvwHjo4r-&amp;_nc_oc=AdovIpyhXZUYQAqnE82JqZ-y7gN_qhGBh-t0WFDCiGiof1M1nPdE7ciPKCsiBkMigmE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=6JNmxJrnTWHJEL0Cnp-T7Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy6lElCi8YYNx00xI_QWOuoiXB0g_XP3yNEgPKhOMw6yQ&amp;oe=69C98908" alt="Instagram billede fra @radiohead" /></p><p><strong>@radiohead</strong></p><p>A message from @eobofficial:<br/>
<br/>
I have a new solo album coming out on 22nd May. It is called Blue Morpho - pre-order at the link in profile.<br/>
<br/>
It was co-written and produced with @paulepworth and @riley_mac, and mixed by @benbaptie. Artwork by @brojazz. I’m so grateful for the extraordinary players who helped make it come alive - @philipselway, @dave_okumu_, @eskaonline, @shabakahutchings, @nrammmusic, @dansee28, Crispin Spry Robinson, @yvesfernandez, Luke Mullen, and others. Musicians whose presence changes everything.<br/>
<br/>
A single - also called Blue Morpho - is out today, with a video.<br/>
<br/>
There’s a short film too, shot in Wales, where much of the album was written, recorded and dreamt up. These songs came out of a dark place, but as Wendell Berry writes, ‘the dark, too, blooms and sings, and is traveled by dark feet and dark wings.’ There was deep beauty and a profound sense of grace in that place.<br/>
<br/>
I’m pleased to announce that there will be screening events for the film held in London - 24th March, Paris - 25th March and Oxford - 26th March. Sign up to my mailing list - link in profile - for a chance to attend London or Paris. Tickets for Oxford on sale soon.<br/>
<br/>
Later in the year, we will be playing these songs live. We would love to share them with you in a room somewhere out there.<br/>
<br/>
Thank you.<br/>
<br/>
With love and gratitude,<br/>
<br/>
🙏 Ed</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/652765451_886044817770760_5171870049393475269_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NDgzNjcwMTc2MDA2MzQ4Mw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=PUTwYjecXlsQ7kNvwHjo4r-&amp;_nc_oc=AdovIpyhXZUYQAqnE82JqZ-y7gN_qhGBh-t0WFDCiGiof1M1nPdE7ciPKCsiBkMigmE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=6JNmxJrnTWHJEL0Cnp-T7Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy6lElCi8YYNx00xI_QWOuoiXB0g_XP3yNEgPKhOMw6yQ&amp;oe=69C98908" alt="Instagram billede fra @radiohead" /></p><p><strong>@radiohead</strong></p><p>A message from @eobofficial:<br/>
<br/>
I have a new solo album coming out on 22nd May. It is called Blue Morpho - pre-order at the link in profile.<br/>
<br/>
It was co-written and produced with @paulepworth and @riley_mac, and mixed by @benbaptie. Artwork by @brojazz. I’m so grateful for the extraordinary players who helped make it come alive - @philipselway, @dave_okumu_, @eskaonline, @shabakahutchings, @nrammmusic, @dansee28, Crispin Spry Robinson, @yvesfernandez, Luke Mullen, and others. Musicians whose presence changes everything.<br/>
<br/>
A single - also called Blue Morpho - is out today, with a video.<br/>
<br/>
There’s a short film too, shot in Wales, where much of the album was written, recorded and dreamt up. These songs came out of a dark place, but as Wendell Berry writes, ‘the dark, too, blooms and sings, and is traveled by dark feet and dark wings.’ There was deep beauty and a profound sense of grace in that place.<br/>
<br/>
I’m pleased to announce that there will be screening events for the film held in London - 24th March, Paris - 25th March and Oxford - 26th March. Sign up to my mailing list - link in profile - for a chance to attend London or Paris. Tickets for Oxford on sale soon.<br/>
<br/>
Later in the year, we will be playing these songs live. We would love to share them with you in a room somewhere out there.<br/>
<br/>
Thank you.<br/>
<br/>
With love and gratitude,<br/>
<br/>
🙏 Ed</p>]]></content:encoded>
