      <title>Jonny is back with @shyebentzur and the Rajasthan Express for their new album, R...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DVq27WhDO9W/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/649228792_18446840053110762_7397682964199296542_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0OTEzMDQwNDY3OTA1MzE0MjE4NDQ2ODQwMDUwMTEwNzYy.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwMTR4MTgwMi5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=H_PDCeWVKM4Q7kNvwEtSmxc&amp;_nc_oc=Adq-XzrffpKfa-mReY8eSoFDbq2-r50jxYK3s92i-_RpXpxjlDt4N3jgnhPcOAND6WI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=6JNmxJrnTWHJEL0Cnp-T7Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxuKmXMGo92TIiNptLusOhNoCRse2otV01737vG6pX_Kg&amp;oe=69C9A75F" alt="Instagram billede fra @radiohead" /></p><p><strong>@radiohead</strong></p><p>Jonny is back with @shyebentzur and the Rajasthan Express for their new album, Ranjha, to be released through @world_circuit_records on 8th May 2026, together with first single Ranjha. <br/>
<br/>
Produced by @sampettsdavies and recorded at Jonny’s Oxfordshire studio, Ranjha is the follow-up to the critically acclaimed Junun, which recently had its tenth anniversary. <br/>
<br/>
Ranjha is available to pre-order at the link in profile on CD, download and a special red and coral splatter gatefold vinyl with a limited edition signed print. In addition, Ranjha and Junun come together with a 32-page newspaper zine with imagery spanning the two records and an essay from Jonny about the project.<br/>
<br/>
The title track Ranjha is accompanied by a short film made by Ian Patrick and you can find it at the link in profile.</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/649228792_18446840053110762_7397682964199296542_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0OTEzMDQwNDY3OTA1MzE0MjE4NDQ2ODQwMDUwMTEwNzYy.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwMTR4MTgwMi5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=H_PDCeWVKM4Q7kNvwEtSmxc&amp;_nc_oc=Adq-XzrffpKfa-mReY8eSoFDbq2-r50jxYK3s92i-_RpXpxjlDt4N3jgnhPcOAND6WI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=6JNmxJrnTWHJEL0Cnp-T7Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxuKmXMGo92TIiNptLusOhNoCRse2otV01737vG6pX_Kg&amp;oe=69C9A75F" alt="Instagram billede fra @radiohead" /></p><p><strong>@radiohead</strong></p><p>Jonny is back with @shyebentzur and the Rajasthan Express for their new album, Ranjha, to be released through @world_circuit_records on 8th May 2026, together with first single Ranjha. <br/>
<br/>
Produced by @sampettsdavies and recorded at Jonny’s Oxfordshire studio, Ranjha is the follow-up to the critically acclaimed Junun, which recently had its tenth anniversary. <br/>
<br/>
Ranjha is available to pre-order at the link in profile on CD, download and a special red and coral splatter gatefold vinyl with a limited edition signed print. In addition, Ranjha and Junun come together with a 32-page newspaper zine with imagery spanning the two records and an essay from Jonny about the project.<br/>
